data.description:
Welcome to Runaway Bay, a golfer and fisherman's paradise!  Runaway Bay is nestled around Lake Bridgeport and is home to Runaway Bay
Golf Club and Resort 18-hole golf course, marina and public boat ramps.  This cute 3 bedroom, 2 bath home boast a large living area with vaulted ceiling and open concept to the dining & kitchen area, and split bedroom floorplan. Brand new laminated hardwood floors, and carpet.  Foundation work just completed with a transferrable lifetime warrant. Located on a quiet street with only 5 other homes. The fenced backyard has a storage building for lawn equipment​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ storage.
